e the getObjectProperty method-name fallback. I wonder if there are uncovered call sites in active?\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_co54KTg5agOI0iZUx0Dvg8is|fc_04df655644feee400169fcd422b51c8195acc6ff0073ce7e27", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "git status --short"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 720, "output": 1416, "cacheRead": 60928, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 63064, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778177021405, "responseId": "resp_04df655644feee400169fcd408ab4c81958ca858889f061a69"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_co54KTg5agOI0iZUx0Dvg8is|fc_04df655644feee400169fcd422b51c8195acc6ff0073ce7e27", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": " M metadata/plexus/plexus-utils/index.json\n D tests/src/plexus/plexus-utils/1.0-alpha-2/src/test/java/plexus/plexus_utils/ClassMapInnerMethodInfoTest.java\n D tests/src/plexus/plexus-utils/1.0-alpha-2/src/test/java/plexus/plexus_utils/ClassMapTest.java\n D tests/src/plexus/plexus-utils/1.0-alpha-2/src/test/java/plexus/plexus_utils/MethodMapTest.java\n M tests/src/plexus/plexus-utils/1.0-alpha-2/src/test/java/plexus/plexus_utils/ReflectionUtilsTest.java\n D tests/src/plexus/plexus-utils/1.0-alpha-2/src/test/java/plexus/plexus_utils/ReflectionValueExtractorTest.java\n M tests/src/plexus/plexus-utils/1.0-alpha-2/src/test/java/plexus/plexus_utils/ReflectorTest.java\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778177059592}]}
